12
00:00:24,660 --> 00:00:25,660
(Representative works: Zhao Ran Fu Li,
Zhi Jing Dong Feng Xue,)

13
00:00:25,660 --> 00:00:26,580
(Di Liu Ci Gong Lue,
Xin Dong Hai Qing Gao Su Wo)

14
00:00:26,620 --> 00:00:28,620
I'm really glad to be here,
meeting everyone

15
00:00:28,620 --> 00:00:30,430
