16
00:00:30,700 --> 00:00:31,230
Hello everyone,

17
00:00:31,230 --> 00:00:32,670
I'm actor Wang Gege.

18
00:00:32,900 --> 00:00:33,900
(Wang Gege: Chinese mainland actress)

19
00:00:33,900 --> 00:00:35,020
(Representative works: Zhao Ran Fu Li,
Zhi Jing Dong Feng Xue,)

20
00:00:35,020 --> 00:00:36,020
