23
00:00:40,590 --> 00:00:42,020
(A little excited)
in an observation room.

24
00:00:42,020 --> 00:00:43,310
It feels strangely fascinating.

25
00:00:43,310 --> 00:00:43,860
Yeah.

26
00:00:43,950 --> 00:00:45,860
Looking forward to them
in Live and Love.

27
00:00:46,430 --> 00:00:47,070
Three, two, one.

28
00:00:48,500 --> 00:00:51,420
(01:00 Xuan Cheng
walks Liu Jiayi back to her room)

29
00:00:51,430 --> 00:00:52,270
Let's head over there.

30
00:00:52,270 --> 00:00:54,700
Xuan Cheng is being pretty proactive.

31
00:00:55,140 --> 00:00:56,590
Wait, are they now...

32
00:00:57,140 --> 00:00:58,070
on a date?

33
00:00:58,140 --> 00:00:59,180
(Just asking)

34
00:00:59,180 --> 00:00:59,630
No.

35
00:00:59,820 --> 00:01:01,750
He wants to seize this chance

36
00:01:01,750 --> 00:01:03,310
to talk with her more.

37
00:01:04,180 --> 00:01:06,270
But Liu Jiayi doesn't seem
very resistant either.

38
00:01:07,630 --> 00:01:09,430
Honestly, I don't feel like
talking to them.

39
00:01:09,430 --> 00:01:10,950
Because all I can think about is you.

40
00:01:10,950 --> 00:01:12,700
What might happen to you?

41
00:01:12,700 --> 00:01:13,630
What might happen on your date?

42
00:01:13,990 --> 00:01:14,780
So straight.

43
00:01:14,980 --> 00:01:17,260
(Loving this direct approach)

44
00:01:17,420 --> 00:01:18,030
He's disappointed,

45
00:01:18,030 --> 00:01:19,990
but not in a really down kind of way.

46
00:01:19,990 --> 00:01:21,820
He's actually quite direct and brave.

47
00:01:22,350 --> 00:01:23,030
Being direct...

48
00:01:23,390 --> 00:01:25,390
Honestly, most girls
respond well to that.

49
00:01:26,500 --> 00:01:28,740
You can tell
from Liu Jiayi's expression.

50
00:01:29,230 --> 00:01:30,770
(She's into it)
She finds him adorable, too.

51
00:01:31,420 --> 00:01:32,860
I want you to know

52
00:01:32,860 --> 00:01:34,310
I really like you.

53
00:01:36,670 --> 00:01:39,390
She might feel bad for Xuan Cheng.

54
00:01:39,390 --> 00:01:40,030
(Blind guess)

55
00:01:40,030 --> 00:01:41,860
But that has nothing to do
with romantic liking.

56
00:01:42,630 --> 00:01:44,420
(I disagree)
Caring is also a kind of liking.

57
00:01:44,670 --> 00:01:45,780
What if someone

58
00:01:45,780 --> 00:01:46,990
you initially had no feelings for

59
00:01:46,990 --> 00:01:48,710
expresses their heart to you

60
00:01:48,710 --> 00:01:49,540
and deeply moves you?

61
00:01:49,540 --> 00:01:50,310
Would you like him?

62
00:01:51,100 --> 00:01:52,950
That's how it is when people connect.

63
00:01:52,950 --> 00:01:54,350
The feelings build up gradually.

64
00:01:56,100 --> 00:01:56,950
Then tomorrow, I must win.

65
00:01:57,350 --> 00:01:57,630
I need to...

66
00:01:58,350 --> 00:01:59,910
I'll fight with everything
I've got to win.

67
00:02:00,180 --> 00:02:01,500
Just don't get yourself hurt.

68
00:02:01,500 --> 00:02:01,990
I don't care.

69
00:02:01,990 --> 00:02:02,780
Even if I get hurt, I still have to win.

70
00:02:03,540 --> 00:02:04,140
I must win.

71
00:02:04,590 --> 00:02:05,820
I just like it when it's you.

72
00:02:06,460 --> 00:02:07,500
Just you and me, alone together.

73
00:02:08,270 --> 00:02:09,060
Not with anyone else.

74
00:02:10,710 --> 00:02:11,910
I really like

75
00:02:11,910 --> 00:02:13,180
(Domineering + Direct approach)
Xuan Cheng's personality.

76
00:02:13,500 --> 00:02:14,500
Your liking is useless.

77
00:02:14,500 --> 00:02:15,950
Liu Jiayi has to like him.

78
00:02:16,460 --> 00:02:17,590
That's why I really admire him.

79
00:02:17,590 --> 00:02:19,830
That all-or-nothing vibe he has.

80
00:02:19,830 --> 00:02:20,390
Yeah.

81
00:02:21,230 --> 00:02:22,550
Anyway, I'm not letting you leave.

82
00:02:25,470 --> 00:02:26,830
(Looks promising) Got some feedback.

83
00:02:26,830 --> 00:02:27,390
Smiling.

84
00:02:27,980 --> 00:02:28,590
Feeling secretly thrilled.

85
00:02:28,590 --> 00:02:30,500
(He's loving it)

86
00:02:30,500 --> 00:02:32,310
If I were sent to that...

87
00:02:32,310 --> 00:02:32,670
mystery date today,

88
00:02:32,670 --> 00:02:33,780
I'd definitely tell them I'm not going.

89
00:02:34,470 --> 00:02:35,340
I'm not going.

90
00:02:36,110 --> 00:02:36,830
For sure.

91
00:02:37,260 --> 00:02:38,500
You're totally going.

92
00:02:39,190 --> 00:02:40,500
(Dating show newbie viewer: can't comprehend)
Feels like he's not

93
00:02:40,500 --> 00:02:41,590
Liu Jiayi's type.

94
00:02:42,260 --> 00:02:43,590
I'm not going!

95
00:02:43,590 --> 00:02:44,310
I said it right then

96
00:02:44,310 --> 00:02:45,550
that I didn't want to draw

97
00:02:45,980 --> 00:02:46,950
(Newbie viewer's personal take)
the first one.

98
00:02:46,950 --> 00:02:48,260
She's been holding back.

99
00:02:48,260 --> 00:02:49,860
Keeping her distance.

100
00:02:50,670 --> 00:02:52,230
I think she's watching closely.

101
00:02:52,230 --> 00:02:53,620
When faced with someone so direct,

102
00:02:53,620 --> 00:02:54,390
she'd wonder

103
00:02:55,340 --> 00:02:57,340
whether what he said was real or not.

104
00:02:57,340 --> 00:02:59,190
See how Liu Jiayi isn't even trying

105
00:02:59,190 --> 00:03:00,980
to engage with his language?

106
00:03:01,140 --> 00:03:02,060
(Like two different worlds)

107
00:03:02,060 --> 00:03:03,550
They lack deep communication.

108
00:03:04,030 --> 00:03:05,140
I truly didn't want to go.

109
00:03:05,140 --> 00:03:06,620
My heart only has you.

110
00:03:08,780 --> 00:03:10,060
But still, the vibe was pretty good.

111
00:03:10,060 --> 00:03:11,830
What left a deep impression
on me back then

112
00:03:12,310 --> 00:03:14,140
was when you said you didn't want to go.

113
00:03:14,550 --> 00:03:16,060
Honestly, I was quite happy
hearing that.

114
00:03:16,380 --> 00:03:17,190
(22:00 Before the boys
dig up the colored seashells)

115
00:03:17,190 --> 00:03:18,190
I don't want to go.

116
00:03:20,950 --> 00:03:22,260
See? Liu Jiayi actually...

117
00:03:24,140 --> 00:03:25,830
Girls do respond to this kind of thing.

118
00:03:26,340 --> 00:03:28,380
(Get it)

119
00:03:30,670 --> 00:03:31,830
I take back what I just said.

120
00:03:32,310 --> 00:03:32,950
These shots make me feel

121
00:03:32,950 --> 00:03:33,980
(Taking back what I said)
she seems...

122
00:03:34,590 --> 00:03:35,780
quite into Xuan Cheng.

123
00:03:35,940 --> 00:03:36,780
(Awkward)

124
00:03:36,780 --> 00:03:37,310
Because

125
00:03:37,420 --> 00:03:38,980
Liu Jiayi is

126
00:03:38,980 --> 00:03:40,260
the aloof type.

127
00:03:40,980 --> 00:03:41,420
Yeah.

128
00:03:41,420 --> 00:03:43,420
She's the type who reaches out

129
00:03:43,420 --> 00:03:45,030
to make contact with someone

130
00:03:45,310 --> 00:03:46,590
and observe their response.

131
00:03:47,060 --> 00:03:48,140
If she were as direct as Xuan Cheng,

132
00:03:48,140 --> 00:03:48,830
they'd

133
00:03:49,750 --> 00:03:50,780
have already clashed.

134
00:03:50,780 --> 00:03:51,820
(Perfect balance)

135
00:03:56,140 --> 00:03:57,500
This totally screams "set worker".

136
00:03:57,780 --> 00:03:59,060
(Totally relatable)

137
00:03:59,060 --> 00:04:00,390
Squatting anywhere, anytime.

138
00:04:01,230 --> 00:04:02,980
Personally, I think I'm someone

139
00:04:02,980 --> 00:04:03,700
who falls at first sight.

140
00:04:03,700 --> 00:04:05,190
I'm very subjective,

141
00:04:05,190 --> 00:04:07,310
and I'm not weak in taking initiative.

142
00:04:07,700 --> 00:04:08,950
I go purely by feeling.

143
00:04:08,950 --> 00:04:09,830
(Day 1, girls' affection delivery.
Zhao Enda)

144
00:04:09,830 --> 00:04:11,110
(Feeling first)
It's all about the first impression.

145
00:04:11,750 --> 00:04:13,340
Is there anyone you think
seems pretty nice right now?

146
00:04:14,030 --> 00:04:15,340
Actually, the "sense of security" one

147
00:04:15,340 --> 00:04:15,830
feels really good.

148
00:04:16,260 --> 00:04:17,110
Zhao Enda.

149
00:04:17,110 --> 00:04:17,420
Yeah.

150
00:04:17,980 --> 00:04:19,110
He looks kind of well-behaved.

151
00:04:19,620 --> 00:04:22,860
So in the beginning,
she was always observing

152
00:04:22,860 --> 00:04:24,470
who she liked.

153
00:04:24,620 --> 00:04:25,550
And once she's made up her mind,

154
00:04:25,550 --> 00:04:27,020
(Act once feelings are clear)
she will take the initiative.

155
00:04:27,300 --> 00:04:28,870
But this early observation period

156
00:04:28,870 --> 00:04:30,500
puts her at a disadvantage.

157
00:04:30,500 --> 00:04:31,230
It makes her quite passive.

158
00:04:32,500 --> 00:04:34,230
I always feel that in a group,

159
00:04:35,060 --> 00:04:36,340
the proactive person

160
00:04:36,340 --> 00:04:37,950
gets noticed more easily.

161
00:04:37,950 --> 00:04:38,900
(Proactive people
experience the world first)

162
00:04:38,900 --> 00:04:39,390
But...

163
00:04:40,110 --> 00:04:41,020
if you act proactively

164
00:04:41,020 --> 00:04:43,150
without really knowing the other person,

165
00:04:43,150 --> 00:04:44,580
and you misjudge...

166
00:04:44,580 --> 00:04:45,740
Isn't that wasted effort?

167
00:04:45,740 --> 00:04:46,780
I'm that type, too.

168
00:04:46,780 --> 00:04:48,020
I tend to watch and observe,

169
00:04:48,020 --> 00:04:49,870
which makes me easy
to overlook early on.

170
00:04:51,270 --> 00:04:52,460
I might not even make it to Episode 2

171
00:04:52,460 --> 00:04:53,580
and get cut right away.

172
00:04:54,710 --> 00:04:55,550
From the start,

173
00:04:55,550 --> 00:04:57,300
you've always been my first pick.

174
00:04:58,300 --> 00:04:58,950
Really?

175
00:05:01,830 --> 00:05:02,950
That made him nervous.

176
00:05:06,180 --> 00:05:06,870
Feeling secretly thrilled.

177
00:05:06,870 --> 00:05:07,230
So...

178
00:05:07,230 --> 00:05:08,390
He's secretly thrilled.

179
00:05:08,390 --> 00:05:09,620
(I misunderstood)

180
00:05:09,830 --> 00:05:11,300
Do all guys react like this?

181
00:05:11,300 --> 00:05:12,830
When a girl expresses liking

182
00:05:12,830 --> 00:05:14,870
very directly to him,

183
00:05:15,060 --> 00:05:16,460
regardless of whether
he has feelings for her,

184
00:05:16,460 --> 00:05:17,620
does he always secretly feel pleased?

185
00:05:17,620 --> 00:05:18,830
(Please answer)
He definitely wouldn't be (upset).

186
00:05:18,830 --> 00:05:20,300
Having someone like you is a good thing.

187
00:05:20,340 --> 00:05:20,900
(Totally happy)

188
00:05:20,900 --> 00:05:21,780
Absolutely.

189
00:05:21,780 --> 00:05:22,580
Feels pretty nice.

190
00:05:22,740 --> 00:05:24,580
(Totally happy)

191
00:05:24,710 --> 00:05:25,430
For example,

192
00:05:25,430 --> 00:05:26,580
keep getting to know me

193
00:05:26,580 --> 00:05:27,550
or...?

194
00:05:28,940 --> 00:05:31,380
(Little thoughts exposed)

195
00:05:35,230 --> 00:05:36,990
(My CP might reshuffle)
He's wavering.

196
00:05:36,990 --> 00:05:37,950
What now?

197
00:05:37,950 --> 00:05:39,180
So wishy washy.

198
00:05:41,340 --> 00:05:44,100
(Yang Tinghong, Zhan Jiaming, Zhao Enda)

199
00:05:44,100 --> 00:05:45,580
(Will there be a showdown?)

200
00:05:49,500 --> 00:05:50,230
Hi.

201
00:05:52,580 --> 00:05:53,150
Hello.

202
00:05:53,780 --> 00:05:54,620
(Sigh of relief)

203
00:05:54,620 --> 00:05:55,550
Huang Jiawei, it's fine.

204
00:05:55,550 --> 00:05:56,340
This one's fine.

205
00:05:56,900 --> 00:05:58,340
This has nothing to do
with the two of them.

206
00:05:59,670 --> 00:06:00,500
Go ahead, you chat first.

207
00:06:01,550 --> 00:06:02,300
You chat.

208
00:06:02,300 --> 00:06:03,230
Northeasterner.

209
00:06:03,340 --> 00:06:04,430
(Back to comedy.
Villager chief inspecting)

210
00:06:04,430 --> 00:06:05,300
A total bystander.

211
00:06:07,710 --> 00:06:08,710
He's so funny.

212
00:06:09,300 --> 00:06:10,620
Why is Huang Jiawei so funny?

213
00:06:10,780 --> 00:06:11,990
(Born comedian)

214
00:06:11,990 --> 00:06:13,900
He looked over with admiration.

215
00:06:14,060 --> 00:06:15,180
A teasing glance.

216
00:06:15,180 --> 00:06:16,780
So nothing's going on
among the three of them.

217
00:06:21,550 --> 00:06:23,150
(A lonely villager chief)
They're on an off-island date right now.

218
00:06:23,150 --> 00:06:24,710
Right at this moment.

219
00:06:26,670 --> 00:06:28,500
The villager chief looks
lost in thought.

220
00:06:28,500 --> 00:06:29,150
Yeah.

221
00:06:31,710 --> 00:06:33,430
Honestly, his mind was...

222
00:06:33,430 --> 00:06:36,150
a mess right then.

223
00:06:37,300 --> 00:06:38,340
He was getting pretty restless.

224
00:06:38,340 --> 00:06:40,020
See how he kept staring outside.

225
00:06:41,670 --> 00:06:43,020
It was like he was waiting for someone.

226
00:06:46,620 --> 00:06:49,300
You cooked breakfast so carefully,
yet no one eats it?

227
00:06:49,300 --> 00:06:50,550
You should just go ahead and eat.

228
00:06:51,430 --> 00:06:52,430
Split it between the two of you.

229
00:06:54,390 --> 00:06:55,580
Actually, today's sandwich

230
00:06:55,580 --> 00:06:56,900
was meant for Yan.

231
00:06:56,900 --> 00:06:58,500
But he waited for her so long,
and she never came back.

232
00:06:58,500 --> 00:06:59,950
So everyone shared it.

233
00:07:05,300 --> 00:07:06,430
I feel quite regretful

234
00:07:06,430 --> 00:07:07,340
for him.

235
00:07:07,340 --> 00:07:08,340
Really feel bad for him.

236
00:07:08,340 --> 00:07:09,460
(Heartache for the bro)

237
00:07:10,580 --> 00:07:12,710
That's not what you said
when you were hyped up.

238
00:07:13,300 --> 00:07:14,830
It feels somewhat unfair.

239
00:07:14,830 --> 00:07:15,710
But...

240
00:07:15,710 --> 00:07:17,270
Love starts with that first glance.

241
00:07:17,270 --> 00:07:18,780
Once you fall for someone, that's it.

242
00:07:18,780 --> 00:07:19,430
There's no way around it.

243
00:07:19,430 --> 00:07:20,580
(Love is never fair) The chemistry...

244
00:07:20,580 --> 00:07:21,740
I really feel it's unfair to him.

245
00:07:21,740 --> 00:07:22,870
But I also totally ship

246
00:07:22,870 --> 00:07:24,870
that couple.

247
00:07:24,870 --> 00:07:26,710
(Torn between both)
Love doesn't play by the rules.

248
00:07:27,740 --> 00:07:28,270
I'm really curious.

249
00:07:28,270 --> 00:07:29,950
Do you still see me clearly
with those sunglasses on?

250
00:07:33,830 --> 00:07:34,740
Yeah, crystal clear.

251
00:07:36,230 --> 00:07:36,900
Why?

252
00:07:37,430 --> 00:07:38,300
Just wondering.

253
00:07:38,300 --> 00:07:39,430
Because I can't see you clearly.

254
00:07:43,700 --> 00:07:45,460
(Perfect match)

255
00:07:46,460 --> 00:07:48,390
Handsome guy, beautiful girl.
Very pleasing to the eye.

256
00:07:48,390 --> 00:07:49,780
(Can't help but ship)

257
00:07:50,390 --> 00:07:51,180
Oh no.

258
00:07:52,060 --> 00:07:53,780
Feels like Jiawei has no chance now.

259
00:07:54,150 --> 00:07:55,710
We're both wearing white shoes.

260
00:07:55,710 --> 00:07:56,340
What a coincidence.

261
00:07:56,830 --> 00:07:57,740
Really.

262
00:07:57,740 --> 00:07:58,780
(Like entering an idol drama scene)
What a coincidence.

263
00:07:59,710 --> 00:08:01,340
The liking is so obvious.

264
00:08:01,340 --> 00:08:02,060
(Completely natural reaction)

265
00:08:02,110 --> 00:08:03,990
You can see the sparkle in her eyes.

266
00:08:03,990 --> 00:08:04,580
The girl...

267
00:08:06,150 --> 00:08:07,110
So blue.

268
00:08:07,620 --> 00:08:09,990
And the sand is so white and beautiful.

269
00:08:10,500 --> 00:08:12,180
This moment must feel perfect.

270
00:08:12,180 --> 00:08:13,150
Blue sky and white clouds.

271
00:08:13,150 --> 00:08:14,500
The beach and the sea.

272
00:08:14,500 --> 00:08:16,150
And the person you like
right next to you.

273
00:08:16,150 --> 00:08:17,150
It's the ambiguous phase.

274
00:08:17,780 --> 00:08:19,870
You seriously don't remember
Huang Jiawei at all?

275
00:08:20,780 --> 00:08:23,110
(Why bring that up?)
When you ship others, just ship properly.

276
00:08:23,620 --> 00:08:25,620
He's all I can think about right now.

277
00:08:25,620 --> 00:08:26,500
